        {
          "text": "已知技术要点",
          "id": "node_34",
          "note": "从实践中积累的关键知识",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "USB 数据流水线",
              "id": "node_35",
              "note": "FPGA output_fifo → FT600 internal FIFO → USB bus → Host driver buffer → App。 USB host controller 主动从 FT600 拉取数据，不等 FT_ReadPipe 调用。"
            },
            {
              "text": "残留数据清理",
              "id": "node_36",
              "note": "每次新采集前必须 flush 整个 pipeline！ FT600 FIFO: FT_AbortPipe + FT_FlushPipe Driver buffer: FT_FlushPipe FPGA output_fifo: FPGA 侧 reset"
            },
            {
              "text": "已修复 Bug: isFirstRead",
              "id": "node_37",
              "note": "部分 header 解析时 isFirstRead flag 未正确设置， 导致间歇性 error code 0x0003。已修复。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
